			<p>Teklab, specialists in <strong>liquid level sensorsÂ </strong>and controllers, have a wide range of liquid level sensors based on digital technology in their portfolio in order to meet the growing market demand.</p>
<p>All the liquid level sensors are low cost, high technology products and have undergone stringent quality control tests.</p>
<p>They are programmable by microcontroller and their body material is compatible with most common chemical agents, food, beverage, oils and fuel.</p>

